1978;;Angela;;Canadian;;Boris Sagal;;Sophia Loren, Steve Railsback;;drama;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Angela_(1978_film);;A war vet finds out that a former prostitute had his baby. Doubting it's his, he gives it away, so she reports him. 20 years later, she still wants to find her son. She meets a young man and falls in love, but the vet's prison term ends.